Installing and compiling BfdAda
===============================

To compiler BfdAda you'll need:

 - an Ada compiler (GNAT or gcc 3.4/4.0).

 - the binutils 2.16 installed for developpment
   (you need the bfd.h include; see binutils-dev package on debian)


Run the GNU configure command and build the library:

  $ ./configure
  $ make


